lt;strong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> 元素可被用来通过 JavaScript（<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\">Canvas</a> API 或 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebGL_API\">WebGL</a> API）绘制图形及图形动画。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p>本元素支持<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\">全局属性</a>。</p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"height\"><a id=\"attr-height\" href=\"#attr-height\"><b><code>height</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>该元素占用空间的高度，以 CSS 像素（px）表示，默认为 150。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"moz-opaque\"><a id=\"attr-moz-opaque\" href=\"#attr-moz-opaque\"><b><code>moz-opaque</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>通过设置这个属性，来控制 canvas 元素是否半透明。如果你不想 canvas 元素被设置为半透明，使用这个元素将可以优化浏览器绘图性能。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"width\"><a id=\"attr-width\" href=\"#attr-width\"><b><code>width</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>该元素占用空间的宽度，以 CSS 像素（px）表示，默认为 300。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"注意事项","title":"注意事项","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"标签需要闭合","title":"标签需要闭合","isH3":true,"content":"<p>不同于 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\"><code>&lt;img&gt;</code></a> 元素， <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a>元素需要有闭合标签 (<code>&lt;/canvas&gt;</code>).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"设置画布_canvas_的大小","title":"设置画布 (canvas) 的大小","isH3":true,"content":"<p>直接在 html 标签中设置 width 和 height 属性或者使用 JavaScript 来指定画布尺寸，这将改变一个画布的水平像素和垂直像素数，就像定义了一张图片的大小一样。</p>\n<p>可以使用 CSS 的 width 和 height 以在渲染期间缩放图像以适应样式大小，就像&lt;img&gt;元素一样。如果您发现&lt;canvas&gt;元素中展示的内容变形，您可以通过&lt;canvas&gt;自带的 height 和 width 属性进行相关设置，而不要使用 CSS。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"最大的画布尺寸","title":"最大的画布尺寸","isH3":true,"content":"<p>画布的最大的尺寸取决于浏览器，下表的结论来自别处 (e.g. <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/6081483/maximum-size-of-a-canvas-element\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Stack Overflow</a>):</p>\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>浏览器</th>\n      <th>最大高度</th>\n      <th>最大宽度</th>\n      <th>最大面积</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Chrome</td>\n      <td>32,767 pixels</td>\n      <td>32,767 pixels</td>\n      <td>268,435,456 pixels (i.e., 16,384 x 16,384)</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Firefox</td>\n      <td>32,767 pixels</td>\n      <td>32,767 pixels</td>\n      <td>472,907,776 pixels (i.e., 22,528 x 20,992)</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Safari</td>\n      <td>32,767 pixels</td>\n      <td>32,767 pixels</td>\n      <td>268,435,456 pixels (i.e., 16,384 x 16,384)</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>IE</td>\n      <td>8,192 pixels</td>\n      <td>8,192 pixels</td>\n      <td>?</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>canvas</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>300<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>300<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  抱歉，您的浏览器不支持 canvas 元素\n （这些内容将会在不支持<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>canvas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>元素的浏览器或是禁用了 JavaScript 的浏览器内渲染并展现）\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>canvas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"javascript","title":"JavaScript","isH3":true,"content":"<p>使用<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/getContext\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.getContext()</code></a>获得一个绘图上下文并开始绘制</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> canvas <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'canvas'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> ctx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getContext</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'2d'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>fillStyle <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'green'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">fillRect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"结果","title":"结果","isH3":true,"content":"<iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"示例 sample\" id=\"frame_示例\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas/_sample_.%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"无障碍","title":"无障碍","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> 元素本身只是一个位图，不提供任何绘制对象的信息。画布内容不像 HTML 那样具有语义并能暴露给无障碍工具。以下指南可以帮助您更方便地访问它。</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Hit_regions_and_accessibility\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">MDN Hit regions and accessability</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/WAI/PF/HTML/wiki/Canvas_Accessibility_Use_Cases\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Canvas accessibility use cases</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/html/wg/wiki/AddedElementCanvas\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Canvas element accessibility issues</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://developer.paciellogroup.com/blog/2012/06/html5-canvas-accessibility-in-firefox-13/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5 Canvas Accessibility in Firefox 13 – by Steve Faulkner</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/scripting.html#best-practices\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Best practices for interactive canvas elements</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/canvas.html#the-canvas-element","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"html.elements.canvas"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.canvas","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\">MDN canvas portal</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial\">Canvas tutorial</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://simon.html5.org/dump/html5-canvas-cheat-sheet.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Canvas cheat sheet</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Demos#canvas\">Canvas-related demos</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/library/archive/documentation/AudioVideo/Conceptual/HTML-canvas-guide/Introduction/Introduction.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Canvas introduction by Apple</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"注意事项","id":"注意事项"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"无障碍","id":"无障碍"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"<canvas> 元素可被用来通过 JavaScript（Canvas API 或 WebGL API）绘制图形及图形动画。","popularity":0.0008,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<canvas>: The Graphics Canvas element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"canvas","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<canvas> : l'élément de canevas graphique","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<canvas>: グラフィックキャンバス要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<canvas>: 그래픽 캔버스 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"canvas","locale":"pt-